I&#039;ve been having this problem for 2 weeks now and no solution has worked for me, from forcing re-patches to changing admin settings... 

I&#039;m on a mac El Capitan (yes i know....) and league stopped opening for me altogether at around new years.. What i would do is double click the league icon and Userkernel would pop up on the dock then immediately disappear, LoLLauncher would follow suit, then LolPatcherUx would appear for about 10 seconds (the icon not the patcher) and then just disappear.

I&#039;ve tried countless solutions but none of them have been working for me... I eventually resorted to uninstalling LoL and reinstalling but after downloading league installer for OCE I got the exact same problem, i went into the file itself and found the LolPatcherUx icon with a grey circle with a bar across it and it said:

 &quot;You can&rsquo;t open the application &ldquo;LoLPatcherUx.app&rdquo; because it may be damaged or incomplete.&quot;

 WHAT?! please if anyone has had this problem or think they know a fix to it feel free to comment...

